fields.name: Under Armour Men's Medal Golf Glove
fields.description: The Under Armour glove is lightweight and breathable to give you a more natural feel as you play golf. The synthetic material offers maximum comfort and traction with a textured palm to enhance grip even further during the golf swing. The glove is enriched with stretch to ensure more performance and has a built-in closure tab for a personalised fit.

fields.name: Brand Fusion Wooden Golf Tees 53mm - 125 Pack
fields.description: This wooden tee is strong and robust and comes in a pack of 125 tees to ensure you have enough tees to last you for numerous rounds of golf. The tee has a standard design to allow you to adjust to different heights and are highly visible to help you find after your shot.

fields.name: Brand Fusion Rake & Golf Ball Retriever
fields.description: Keep your golf course bunkers in top condition with this handy accessory which fits neatly in to your golf bag. It ensures you can look after the bunker and can also be used as a ball retiever to get your golf ball from any hazards. It is lightweight and sturdy and the head can be folded to save space.
